import React from 'react'
import {ChakraProvider, Container, Box, Stack, Text, Heading} from '@chakra-ui/react'

const Header = () => {
    return (
        <ChakraProvider>
            <Container>
                <Stack direction="row">
                    <Box>
                        <Heading>Home</Heading>
                    </Box>
                    <Box w="23px" h="23px" bg="tomato"></Box>
                </Stack>
            </Container>
        </ChakraProvider>
    )
}


export default Header
